Code and per-prediction outputs in this repository are provided for the purpose of
double-blind peer review.

They are intended for release under a permissive open-source license (MIT or
Apache-2.0). The copyright holder is withheld during anonymous review and will be
stated, together with the chosen license text, in the public release upon acceptance.

No warranty. Third-party datasets (VizWiz-VQA, VQAv2) and model weights are governed by
their own licenses and are not redistributed here.
